<doc f='include/llvm-6.0/llvm/IR/BasicBlock.h' l='343'>/// \brief Notify the BasicBlock that the predecessor \p Pred is no longer
  /// able to reach it.
  ///
  /// This is actually not used to update the Predecessor list, but is actually
  /// used to update the PHI nodes that reside in the block.  Note that this
  /// should be called while the predecessor still refers to this block.</doc>
